  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, he went to England to learn-- after-- he-- he had already become a master tailor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he went to England to perfect his work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I met him in England-- in London.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How long did you know him before you were married?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's quite a story, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My girlfriend and I wondered what to do one Saturday night, and we looked in the which is comparable to the here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to this dance at Boots Cafe-- well, it was actually above Boots Pharmacy on Regent Street in London, and that's where I met my husband.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, it's a longer story than that, but I'm not going to go into all that--the long story, I don't think.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I met him there, and we started to date.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he went back to Norway, and he just casually asked me if I would come to Norway for a holiday.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought that would be fun, not thinking that I would end up marrying him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I thought that it would be fun to go to Norway.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went there at the beginning of the summer, and I stayed with his family a few weeks, and then we decided to get married.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So actually, I know-- only knew him for just a few weeks, because we got married in September of that same year.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, when I was in Norway and we decided to get married, and I wrote and told my parents that we'd decided to get married, and they say, a nice Jewish girl gets married from her own home.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So no way are you going to get married in Norway.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, we have booked your wedding for September the 13th.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
